item.title: Data and Cookie Policy
item.description: Data and Cookie Policy This data and cookie policy explains how SWIEST (“we”, “us”, or “our”) collects, uses, and shares your personal data when you visit or use our website https://swiest.com . Please read this policy carefully and contact us if you have any questions. What data do we collect? We collect personal data that you provide to us when you use our website, such as your name, email address, phone number, or payment information.
